  summer   external linksedit biography portal books portal business and economics portal complementary and alternative medicine portal criminal justice portal health and fitness portal medicine portal radio portal snooker portal television in the united states portal authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     musicbrainz fffbc nla  ndl  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlekevintrudeauoldid categories  birthsliving peopleamerican adopteesamerican businesspeopleamerican businesspeople convicted of crimesamerican conspiracy theoristsamerican health and wellness writersamerican people convicted of fraudamerican prisoners and detaineesamerican salespeopleamerican television personalitiesamerican whitecollar criminalsantivaccination activistsconfidence trickstersconsumer fraudcriminals from massachusettsinfomercialspeople from dupage county illinoispeople from lynn massachusettspeople from zürichpeople in alternative medicinepool coaches managers and promoterspseudoscientific diet advocateshidden categories wikipedia articles needing clarification from november webarchive template wayback linkswikipedia articles needing clarification from august all articles with dead external linksarticles with dead external links from september articles with dead external links from december wikipedia pending changes protected pages level articles which use infobox templates with no data rowsarticles with hcardsblp articles lacking sources from november all blp articles lacking sourcesall articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statements from march articles with unsourced statements from march wikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles with isni identifierswikipedia articles with musicbrainz identifierswikipedia articles with nla identifiersarticles with inconsistent citation formats navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article 