transaction with covidien plc mr trudeau joined covidien in february  as a senior vice president and president of its pharmaceuticals business he joined covidien from bayer healthcare llc the us healthcare business of bayer ag where he served as chief executive officer from  to  in addition he served as president of the global specialty medicine business unit in  prior to joining bayer in  mr trudeau headed the immunoscience division at bristolmyers squibb during his plus years at bristolmyers squibb he served in multiple senior roles including president of the asiapacific region president and general manager of canada and general managermanaging director in the united kingdom mr trudeau was also with abbott laboratories serving in a variety of executive positions from  to  mr trudeau became a member of the te connectivity ltd board of directors in  he was appointed a trustee of the donald danforth plant science center in st louis in december  mr trudeau holds a bachelor’s degree in chemical engineering and an mba both from the university of michigan back building on our heritage nearly  years of quality integrity and service learn more our culture from philanthropic efforts to advocacy initiatives we are living our hallmarks throughout our communities learn how kitchen utensils pepper mills glassware  trudeau canada where to buy retailer login about us faq contact us  canada en canada en canada fr usa international en international fr  canada en canada en canada fr usa international en international fr where to buy retailer login about us faq contact us coffee is a way of life morning or afternoon it’s always time to savour the taste of a freshly brewed coffee coffee and tea javascript seems to be disabled in your browser you must have javascript enabled in your browser to utilize the functionality of this website egg tools lets get cracking discover fruit tools press cut or zest discover about us at trudeau corporation we are proud to be recognized as a leader in 