gs infomercial king kevin trudeau from jail — for now chicago suntimes archived from the original on february   retrieved september     kevin trudeau jailed then released after spending  on two haircuts the christian science monitor september   retrieved september     tv pitchman pleads for mercy jailed anyway the bismarck tribune october   retrieved october     kirby adam november   us tv pitchman trudeau found guilty of criminal contempt retrieved november     meisner jason november   tv pitchman kevin trudeau found guilty of contempt ordered held chicago tribune retrieved november     janssen kim november   kevin trudeau already in jail but nd judge slams cell door chicago sun times archived from the original on december   retrieved november     janssen kim february   infomercial king kevin trudeau’s possessions to be auctioned chicago suntimes archived from the original on march     infamous infomercial king kevin trudeaus secret global club off the market sold to highest bidders khsbcom archive archived  at the wayback machine retrieved april    holland leslie march   television pitchman kevin trudeau is headed to prison cnn retrieved march     meisner jason march   tv pitchman kevin trudeau sentenced to  years in prison chicago tribune retrieved november     infomercial scammer kevin trudeau appeals conviction september   consumeristcom retrieved april    ftc v trudeau appellate brief retrieved december    stempel j february   us tv pitchman kevin trudeau loses appeal of conviction sentence reuterscom retrieved december    kevin trudeau inmate   federal bureau of prisons us dept of justice  a b meisner jason april   prison doesnt keep pitchman off tv convicted huckster maintains airtime and fans chicago tribune retrieved april     judge approves refunds for buyers of kevin trudeau’s diet book wbbm october   retrieved october     natural cures chapter  – i should be dead by nowclarification needed  the gauntlet® news  firm claims diabetes cure thegauntletca arc