deau takes part of this important commitment by manufacturing highquality bpa free bottles and insulated mugs which can be washed and reused over and over x prevention and a cure in our lifetime trudeau corporation continues to support the fight against breast cancer with its gadgets hydration and thermal products available during octobers breast cancer awareness month and throughout the year this collection of gadgets hydration and thermal products are designed exclusively for trudeaus product donation program they are sold in support of breast cancer research initiatives as the company will give a portion of all sales of the designated products to the breast cancer research foundation x warranty trudeaus products are designed and manufactured to meet the highest quality standards in the industry our warranty covers all materials or manufacturing defects under conditions of normal household use and is valid for the period specified on the products packaging to return your defective product and get a replacement or refund please contact our customer service department by filling the following form shoptrudeaucom mugs and bottles wwwshoptrudeaucom for retailers  my account your cart is empty shipping on the go  fuel kitchen gadgets mills  spices bar  home shop by type water bottles desk  travel mugs travel tumblers infusion bottles  accessories coffee  tea at home  onthego hydration bcrf thermal and hydration fuel shop by capacity less than  oz    oz more than  oz shop by price          over  warehouse deals save product best for sport  outdoor activities office travel  in the car shop by type cooking  preparation baking silicone heatresistent stress less easy to use laguiole sets and gifts save now shop by color red green blue orange yellow black silver shop by price          over  warehouse deals save shop by material silicone plastic bpafree stainless steel product best for eggs cheese garlic fruits and vegetables opening cans shop by type pepper mills and salt mi