entally friendly products x reusable thermal mugs  water bottles plastic bottles and styrofoam cups tons of plastic and styrofoam disposables made from petroleumbased chemicals and additives are thrown away every year petroleum is not only becoming an increasingly scarce resource it also causes pollution and toxicity every step of its use  extraction transportation refining and production plastic and styrofoam are not biodegradable and they persist in the environment for hundreds of years causing further pollution reducing consumption of plastic bottles and styrofoam cups by purchasing reusable bottles or thermal mugs is a small step that we can all take to help save the environment trudeau takes part of this important commitment by manufacturing highquality bpa free bottles and insulated mugs which can be washed and reused over and over x prevention and a cure in our lifetime trudeau corporation continues to support the fight against breast cancer with its gadgets hydration and thermal products available during octobers breast cancer awareness month and throughout the year this collection of gadgets hydration and thermal products are designed exclusively for trudeaus product donation program they are sold in support of breast cancer research initiatives as the company will give a portion of all sales of the designated products to the breast cancer research foundation x warranty trudeaus products are designed and manufactured to meet the highest quality standards in the industry our warranty covers all materials or manufacturing defects under conditions of normal household use and is valid for the period specified on the products packaging to return your defective product and get a replacement or refund please contact our customer service department by filling the following form shoptrudeaucom mills and spices wwwshoptrudeaucom for retailers  my account your cart is empty shipping on the go  fuel kitchen gadgets mills  spices bar  home shop by type water bottles des