y us federal trade commission ftc for making false or misleading claims in infomercials promoting his book the weightloss cure they dont want you to know about in  he settled that action by agreeing to pay a  fine and consenting to a lifetime ban on promoting products other than his books via infomercials on nov   the seventh circuit court of appeals upheld a  million fine levied against him for violating that  settlement additionally on remand the district court modified its final order requiring that he post a  million bond before engaging in future infomercial advertisingon march   trudeau was sentenced to  years in prison stemming from his november  criminal contempt convictionwikipedia more combine editionskevin trudeaus books kevin trudeau average rating  ·  ratings ·  reviews ·  distinct works · similar authors natural cures they dont want you to know about  avg rating —  ratings — published  —  editions want to read saving… want to read currently reading read error rating book refresh and try again rate this book clear rating  of  stars of  stars of  stars of  stars of  stars more natural cures revealed  avg rating —  ratings — published  —  editions want to read saving… error rating book refresh and try again rate this book clear rating  of  stars of  stars of  stars of  stars of  stars debt cures they dont want you to know about  avg rating —  ratings — published  —  editions want to read saving… error rating book refresh and try again rate this book clear rating  of  stars of  stars of  stars of  stars of  stars the weight loss cure they dont want you to know about  avg rating —  ratings — published  —  editions want to read saving… error rating book refresh and try again rate this book clear rating  of  stars of  stars of  stars of  stars of  stars free money  avg rating —  ratings — published  —  editions want to read saving… error rating book refresh and try again rate this book clear rating  of  stars of  stars of  stars of  stars of  stars kevin trud